7400:[name]拓巳[line]W-While we can...[%p]
7500:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry, Nishijo.[%p]
7600:[name]セナ[line]You were protecting me, and now you're bleeding so much... Sob...[%p]
7700:Her eyes were soaked with tears. I'd never seen her cry before. Come to think of it, I wasn't sure I'd even thought she was capable of crying.[%p]
7800:And only now, with my hand around her shoulder, did I realize for the first time...[%p]
7900:just how frail her body was. Sena probably wasn't special, either. Real-life girls were just thin, like this.[%p]
8000:Normally she was arrogant, bossy, and always felt eager to step on my face. But... Sena was a girl after all.[%p]
8100:Don't worry, Sena. There's nothing for you to cry about. If we can get the cheat code, I'll be fine. I'll be just fine.[%p]
8200:I clenched my jaw and started to walk.[%p]
8300:Behind me, I could hear a strange noise, and a piercing resonating sound. I didn't look back.[%p]
